<subSubSection pageId="825" pageNumber="826" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="825" pageNumber="826">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="825" pageNumber="826">This species ranges from southeastern Georgia (Fattig 1949: 40; McIntosh County, CNC) to southern Florida (Peck and Thomas 1998: 24), west to southwestern Alabama (Leng 1915: 588; Mobile County, MCZ, USNM); also recorded from the Bahamas (Turnbow and Thomas 2008: 13). The record from Guana Island (Valentine and Ivie 2005: 275) in the British Virgin Islands needs confirmation.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
